  "abstract": {
    "value": "Alkyl allenes were obtained by the reaction of 1-ethynylcycloalkanol acetates with the organocopper reagents, LiMe₂Cu and Li-n-Bu₂Cu. Reactions of steroidal ethynylcarbinol acetates show that the reaction is not stereoselective. The functional group specificity of the organocopper reagents and the scope of the reaction are outlined.",
